# 1957 Delaware State Hornets football team

The 1957 Delaware State Hornets football team represented Delaware State College—now known as Delaware State University—as a member of the Central Intercollegiate Athletic Association (CIAA) in the 1957 college football season. Led by coach Bennie J. George in his second season, the Hornets compiled a 6–2 record.
